title: Jackie & Roy - The Beautiful Sea: songs of sun, sand & s
description:
JACKIE & ROY - THE BEAUTIFUL SEA

songs of sun, sea & sand

"Many of our happiest days were spent by the beautiful sea, on glorious beaches with our daughters, Niki and Dana and many dear friends. To them we dedicate these songs."
-Jackie & Roy

1. By The Beautiful Sea & Home By The Sea
2. Moon Over Miami
3. On A Slowboat To China
4. Sand In My Shoes
5. Zanzibar
6. Dolphin Dance
7. Full Moon
8. Boats
9. Sun On My Face
10. Seashells
11. The Shining Sea
12. Song Of The Boy And The Dolphins
13. By The Beautiful Sea (reprise)

Jackie Cain - vocals and ideas
Roy Kral - piano, vocals, arranger and concepts
Dean Johnson - bass
Terry Clarke - drums
David Samuels - mrimba, vibes
Paul Meyers - guitar
Guillermo Acevedo - percussion
Matt Havilland and Eric Friedlander - cellos
John Simon - musical coordinator, string orchestrator, and trombones on "Sand In My Shoes"

Recorded in NYC in 1998

1999 DRG
